{"tid":274648,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭招募10 000名移民","createTime":"2017-06-07T12:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T03:48:05.000Z","uid":70028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f39ce67a4bd001f840030f64677ca54bbac05e3","tid":274648,"uid":70028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://yo2days.wordpress.com/2017/06/02/%e5%94%94%e9%a7%9b%e6%99%af%e9%b4%bb%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91-%e7%b4%90%e8%a5%bf%e8%98%ad%e6%8b%9b%e5%8b%9f10-000%e5%90%8d%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyo2days.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2F%25e5%2594%2594%25e9%25a7%259b%25e6%2599%25af%25e9%25b4%25bb%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e6%25b0%2591-%25e7%25b4%2590%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e8%2598%25ad%25e6%258b%259b%25e5%258b%259f10-000%25e5%2590%258d%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e6%25b0%2591%2F&d=Lwq37QuzZXg%2B2cZCUkfRWNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=10f6d149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yo2days.wordpress.com/2017/06/02/%e5%94%94%e9%a7%9b%e6%99%af%e9%b4%bb%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91-%e7%b4%90%e8%a5%bf%e8%98%ad%e6%8b%9b%e5%8b%9f10-000%e5%90%8d%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91/</a><br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭的南地大區(Southland)，位於紐西蘭南島的最南端。天然資源豐富、環境冇得輸，但係當地有一個特別難搞嘅問題，就是人口太少，而人口少係因為氣候太凍。呢度每年平均最高氣溫係攝氏14度，最低氣溫係5.5度，平均氣溫都只得10度左右。雖然天氣係凍咗啲，但呢度嘅風景優美、空氣清新、工作多、福利好，非常適合人類居住。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n當地政府計劃，2025年前要留下至少1萬個新移民。原因係當地老年化問題嚴重，未來幾年仲有幾千人等住退休，食飯口多過打工手，咁搞落去真係坐食山崩，引入新移民係冇辦法之中嘅辦法。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n為咗配合政府嘅大計，當地唔少公司已經聯同學校有晒plan，例如紐西蘭南部理工學院（Southern Institute of Technology）表示，到該學校讀書的國際留學生，讀完書之後政府會幫你搵埋工，期望你呢位「專材」留低生活。唔知駛唔駛住夠七年先有身份證呢？<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n講到住，當地嘅樓價格簡直超值，20~30萬紐幣（約100-150萬港紙）就可以買到一間非常豪華嘅house，渣車10分鐘就出到城。喺香港？100萬港紙你連深水埗劏房都買唔起啦。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n講埋環境，南地大區係紐西蘭乃至全世界受污染最小嘅區域，自然環境冇經過人為破壞(可能係某國人少去吧？)，仲有，呢個區嘅海豚、企鵝同海豹仲多過人類，唔駛畀錢都可以日日去海洋公園咁，係咪爽皮先？<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n講到咁吸引，點樣申請？快手click入去呢個網頁睇睇：<a href=\"http://www.sords.co.nz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sords.co.nz&d=Lwq37QuzZXg%2B2cZCUkfRWNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=423cbd34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.sords.co.nz</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;(無錯，係英文。移民得紐西蘭緊係要識英文啦！"},{"pid":"288c676a124e78b77562c05e4745edcdfb35a4e2","tid":274648,"uid":70028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d82fefa5d70fad64335f62f08f983a99ffb40ff","tid":274648,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51c306a8cc51d419d3d6abb9b39847430f6b9be","tid":274648,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:09:23.000Z","msg":"點申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f2a5c5e3974b092caeea9dc89159f562ce7d67","tid":274648,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c31575c7afc9979a295e2639ae025fb1950495","tid":274648,"uid":18944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"唔係只限國內？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1186841788204a58f492cb966910246a50f49834","tid":274648,"uid":70028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"呢啲地方怕唔怕悶死？"},{"pid":"a6fd172eb5392184d7702ed4cae18bb348e1343b","tid":274648,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"好驚去到好似去左鄉下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43daac5e4a54105e1b5075c3d85fe89b92ab91f","tid":274648,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"幾時有得申請<img src=\"/assets/face